132nd MAINE LEGISLATURE
FIRST REGULAR SESSION-2025
Legislative Document No. 1170
H.P. 775 House of Representatives, March 20, 2025
An Act to Make the Maine Redevelopment Land Bank Authority
Responsible for the Transfer and Development of State-owned
Surplus Land
