41 with the Maine Administrative Procedure Act, Title 5, chapter 375, subchapter 2-A to
42 implement this subchapter sections 4751, 4752 and 4753, including eligibility standards
43 for financing under this subchapter sections 4751, 4752 and 4753. The Maine
