15 SUMMARY
1166 This bill replaces the Maine State Housing Authority with the Maine Redevelopment
1177 Land Bank Authority as the state agency responsible for the transfer and development of
1188 state-owned surplus land. The bill also removes an outdated report provision regarding the
1199 Maine State Housing Authority's first option to purchase surplus lands.
